{"tid":589194,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖)派綠帽嘅音樂家又開演奏會喇！！ ！","createTime":"2018-03-11T17:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T18:21:45.000Z","uid":93826,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7722ad64e2d11c8b1e3b32c45ad6778d671085ce","tid":589194,"uid":93826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T17:28:17.000Z","msg":"連登仔係時候醒下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家嘅臭雞嘅層次不停提升 派帽派到痴撚曬線<br />\n你以為拍得耐拖就會好sweet好穩陣 事實上拍咗三 五年一樣大把雞派帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你以為訂埋婚得喇掛 事實上訂埋婚 臭雞一樣可以臨尾玩鳩你 唔撚結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/005632_0b9955ec06be6365e0f62bf819df7586.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F005632_0b9955ec06be6365e0f62bf819df7586.jpg&h=4135ac09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/005649_5f2ce2938073cac34c9b6bbd6eb64d89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F005649_5f2ce2938073cac34c9b6bbd6eb64d89.jpg&h=7433044c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主人家就係呢個派綠帽嘅音樂家--- 吳凱恩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同男朋友拍拖5 6年 婚都訂埋 <br />\nIG post哂婚戒 扮sweet 講撚哂情深深 雨濛濛嘅野 <br />\n男士們自己諗下 拍拖拍到談婚論嫁嘅地步 付出咗咁多野 <br />\n膚淺嘅有金錢付出 做男人日日出去 搵錢買禮物 氹佢開心<br />\n仲有個份感情 邊個可以明白 每日嘅甜言密語 每一個眼神 對話都係愛<br />\n突然間可以話唔結就唔結 點解可以咁撚自私<br />\n<br />\n以下佢同佢條仔嘅相 要圖自己上佢IG睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/005708_2a31fe8d440744c15c4a77e1f2f04eb5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F005708_2a31fe8d440744c15c4a77e1f2f04eb5.jpg&h=9cb42cd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/010812_a249a11c73a02925ef62eddd7a3f89bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F010812_a249a11c73a02925ef62eddd7a3f89bf.jpg&h=dba9af0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完全接受唔撚到呢種人 你可以唔結 你可以兒戲 但唔該唔好累人<br />\n仲有唔好扮受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n情人節仲要post 條YouTube video 話自己無valentine 扮撚哂唔開心咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知係唔係釣緊狗公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事到如今 唯有替佢條仔開心 睇清呢個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/004103_6773e80cba15bac53c9b3534f45e5d3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F004103_6773e80cba15bac53c9b3534f45e5d3c.jpg&h=56224bc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n送埋條LINK比大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4_emJ5slkww\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4_emJ5slkww&d=ZU%2BVxSsGslah%2F71SpSkvf8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=68e5b4b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4_emJ5slkww</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後  想問下有無兄弟有更多呢條臭雞嘅資料<br />\n同埋想同佢講句<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 仆街啦 臭雞！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係最後 同肥屍講嘅 我賭J我一個字都無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5987620c78230f475c12cbe299477522eba38195","tid":589194,"uid":21423,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"repl